  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:0",
      "text": "欢迎来到 RenderMan Fundamentals，这是 Pixar 旗舰 renderer 的官方入门训练。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:2",
      "text": "PxrSurface 基础入门课程（PxrSurface Basics）",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:3",
      "text": "Overview（概览）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:4",
      "text": "本课将对 RenderMan 随附的优秀 Uber shader PxrSurface 做一个基础概览。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:6",
      "text": "在本课中，我们将探索如何正确使用 PxrSurface material 中的 Diffuse lobe，以及何时需要对 ACEScg 或 sRGB texture maps 进行 linearize。",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 27
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:7",
      "text": "Artistic Specular（艺术化高光）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:9",
      "text": "物理高光课程（Physical Specular）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:11",
      "text": "导体与电介质（Conductors & Dielectrics）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:13",
      "text": "虹彩参数课程（Iridescence）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:15",
      "text": "天鹅绒与绒毛（Velvet & Fuzz）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:18",
      "text": "在这节 Glass 课程中，你将学习 Glass lobe 内的所有基础 parameters。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:21",
      "text": "次表面散射课程（Subsurface Scattering）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:22",
      "text": "本课将介绍 RenderMan 中的 Subsurface Scattering，以及 PxrSurface 随附的各种 SSS models。请务必跟随 project file 一起操作！",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:23",
      "text": "PxrSurface 材质分层课程（PxrSurface Layering）",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:24",
      "text": "材质分层课程（Material Layering）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:25",
      "text": "在本课中，学习使用多功能的 PxrLayerSurface material system 创建精细 layered materials 的基础知识。请务必下载",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:26",
      "text": "Midnight Rebel",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:27",
      "text": "Maya project 来跟随学习！",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "a8f69d3239:29",
      "text": "现在你已经掌握了 PxrSurface material 的基本工作方式，下一课我们将了解来自 Industrial Light & Magic 的 MaterialX Lama shading system。",
      "ascii_letters": 64,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    }
  ],
